trans-unit.source: Install or update a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] deployment on a computer.
trans-unit.target: Installere eller oppdatere en [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] distribusjon på en datamaskin.

trans-unit.source: You can use InPlaceHostingManager to write programs that install [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] applications programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke InPlaceHostingManager å skrive programmer som installerer [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmer programmatisk.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use this class in a controlled system management software (SMS) environment or in situations where you need a complex installation that performs a number of pre-installation or post-installation operations on the local computer.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel bruke denne klassen i et miljø med kontrollert systemet administrasjon av programvare (SMS) eller i tilfeller der du trenger en kompleks installasjon som utfører et antall før installasjonen eller etter operasjoner på den lokale datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Generally, you will want to use the members of this class in a specific order: 1.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis, vil du bruke medlemmene av denne klassen i en bestemt rekkefølge: 1.

trans-unit.source: Create a new instance of InPlaceHostingManager.
trans-unit.target: Opprett en ny forekomst av InPlaceHostingManager.

trans-unit.source: Download the deployment manifest by using <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Last ned distribusjon manifestet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>

trans-unit.source: Check that the application can be run with the appropriate permissions by using <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller at programmet kan kjøres med riktige tillatelser ved hjelp av <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>

trans-unit.source: Download and install the application by using <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Last ned og installer programmet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>

trans-unit.source: - If you call any of these parameters out of order, they will throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis du kaller noen av disse parameterne utenfor rekkefølge, vil de Iverksett et unntak.

trans-unit.source: InPlaceHostingManager can install a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application, but cannot execute it.
trans-unit.target: InPlaceHostingManager kan installere en [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmet, men kan ikke kjøre den.

trans-unit.source: Some methods in this class, such as <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.Execute%2A>, are reserved for use when downloading a Windows Presentation Foundation-based application that runs inside a Web browser.
trans-unit.target: Noen metoder på dette class, for eksempel <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.Execute%2A>, er reservert for bruk ved nedlasting av et Windows presentasjon Foundation-basert program som kjører inne i en webleser.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.Execute%2A>

trans-unit.source: To use InPlaceHostingManager to download and install applications, you must make sure that the certificate for signing the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] applications you plan to install is already installed on client computers as a trusted publisher.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil bruke InPlaceHostingManager laste ned og installere programmer, må du kontrollere som sertifikat for signering av [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmene du vil installere allerede er installert på klientdatamaskiner som en klarert utgiver.

trans-unit.source: For more information on trusted publishers, see [Trusted Application Deployment Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil vite mer om klarerte utgivere, se [klarert oversikt over distribusjon av programmet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > There is currently a product limitation that prevents InPlaceHostingManager from working correctly when you debug your code using [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Det er en begrensning for produktet som hindrer at InPlaceHostingManager fungerer når du feilsøker kode ved hjelp av [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: If you debug your application in [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] by using the F5 key, the sample will throw mysterious exceptions when you call <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du feilsøke programmet i [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] via F5 for eksemplet vil throw mystisk unntak når du kaller <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>

trans-unit.source: To debug using [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)], start the application without debugging, and then attach the debugger.
trans-unit.target: Feilsøke ved hjelp av [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)]ved å starte programmet uten feilsøking, og koble feilsøkingsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, you can use another debugger, such as WinDbg.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke en annen debugger, for eksempel WinDbg.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref> to download and install the specified browser-hosted application.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"> </xref> laste ned og installere den angitte leser vertsbaserte applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is used when you want to download a Windows Presentation Foundation-based application that is hosted in a Web browser.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren brukes når du vil laste ned et Windows presentasjon Foundation-basert program som ligger i en webleser.

trans-unit.source: To download Windows Forms-based applications that are deployed using [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)], use the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.%23ctor%2A> constructor with the `launchInHostProcess` parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Laste ned Windows Forms-baserte programmer som er distribuert med [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)], bruk av <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør med den `launchInHostProcess` parameteren satt til `false`.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A Uniform Resource Identifier (<xref:System.Uri>) to a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application's deployment manifest.
trans-unit.target: En Uniform Resource Identifier (<xref:System.Uri>) til en [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmets distribusjon manifestet.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref> can be used only in Windows XP or in later versions of the Windows operating system.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref>kan brukes bare i Windows XP eller nyere versjoner av Windows-operativsystem.

trans-unit.target: Kan ikke sende for den deploymentManifest argumentet.

trans-unit.target: deploymentManifestbruker et URI-skjemaet som ikke støttes av [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref> to download and install the specified application, which can be either a stand-alone Windows Forms-based application or an application hosted in a Web browser.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"> </xref> laste ned og installere den angitte applikasjonen, som kan være et frittstående Windows Forms-basert program eller et program som er vert for en webleser.

trans-unit.source: The Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) to the deployment manifest of the application that will be installed.
trans-unit.target: Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) til manifestfilen distribusjon av programmet installeres.

trans-unit.source: Whether this application will be run in a host, such as a Web browser.
trans-unit.target: Om dette programmet kjøres i en vert, for eksempel en webleser.

trans-unit.source: For a stand-alone application, set this value to <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Sett denne verdien til for et frittstående program <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref> can be used only in Windows XP or in later versions of the Windows operating system.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref>kan brukes bare i Windows XP eller nyere versjoner av Windows-operativsystem.

trans-unit.target: Kan ikke sende for den deploymentManifest argumentet.

trans-unit.target: deploymentManifestbruker et URI-skjemaet som ikke støttes av [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application has the appropriate permissions and platform dependencies to run on the local computer.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] program har riktige tillatelser og plattformen avhengigheter skal kjøres på den lokale datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: You must call AssertApplicationRequirements after <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A> returns successfully.
trans-unit.target: Du må kalle AssertApplicationRequirements etter <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>returnerer ble.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must not call <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A> unless you call AssertApplicationRequirements, and it returns without error.
trans-unit.target: Du må ikke kalle <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>med mindre du kaller AssertApplicationRequirements, og returnerer uten feil.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.DownloadApplicationAsync%2A>

trans-unit.source: Raised if this method is called before the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync*> method.
trans-unit.target: Starter Hvis denne metoden kalles før den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync*>metoden.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync*>

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application has the appropriate permissions and platform dependencies to run on the local computer.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] program har riktige tillatelser og plattformen avhengigheter skal kjøres på den lokale datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: If `grantApplicationTrust` is `true`, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> will grant the application elevated permissions if it requires them.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `grantApplicationTrust` er `true`, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>vil gi programmet privilegerte tillatelser hvis den krever dem.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: This is only possible if <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> is able to grant those permissions.
trans-unit.target: Dette er bare mulig hvis <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>kan gi disse tillatelsene.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: For example, if a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application is being installed as part of a larger package and the installer has been granted full trust, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> will be able to grant the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application full trust.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis en [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmet installeres som en del av en større pakke og installasjonsprogrammet har fått fullstendig klarering <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>kan gi den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmet fullstendig klarering.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: If `grantApplicationTrust` is `false`, the application will not be granted any permissions.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `grantApplicationTrust` er `false`, programmet vil ikke bli gitt tillatelser.

trans-unit.source: If <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, the application will attempt to elevate its permissions to the required level.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>, programmet vil prøve å øke tillatelsene til det nødvendige nivået.

trans-unit.source: Cancels an asynchronous download operation.
trans-unit.target: Avbryter en asynkron nedlastingen.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>.
trans-unit.target: Kall avhending når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Fjerningsmetoden forlater den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter å avhending, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>ble bruker.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall fjerne før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager>

trans-unit.source: Downloads an application update in the background.
trans-unit.target: Laster ned en appoppdateringen i bakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: You must call this method after calling <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du må kalle denne metoden etter kaller <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>

trans-unit.source: Raised if this method is called before the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync*> and <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements*> methods.
trans-unit.target: Starter Hvis denne metoden kalles før den <> </> *> og <> </> *> metoder.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the application has finished downloading to the local computer.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når programmet er nedlastet til den lokale datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: If you are installing a Windows Forms-based application, you will need to instruct users to launch the application themselves; you cannot start Windows Forms-based applications programmatically by using the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.Execute%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du installerer et Windows Forms-basert program, må du be brukere å starte programmet seg; Du kan ikke starte Windows Forms-baserte programmer programmatisk ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.Execute%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.Execute%2A>

trans-unit.source: Occurs when there is a change in the status of an application or manifest download.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når det er en endring i statusen for en nedlasting av programmet eller manifest.

trans-unit.source: In a console application, events are assigned to threads from a thread pool.
trans-unit.target: I en konsoll applikasjon tilordnes hendelser tråder fra en trådutvalget.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you might receive progress update events out of order, with a subsequent event showing a decrease compared with a previous event.
trans-unit.target: Derfor kan du få pågår oppdateringshendelser utenfor gyldig område, med et etterfølgende hendelse som viser dårligere sammenlignes med en tidligere hendelse.

trans-unit.source: You will not see such behavior in a Windows Forms-based application, because events in Windows Forms are processed sequentially out of the user interface (UI) thread's message queue.
trans-unit.target: Slik virkemåte i Windows Forms-basert program vises ikke fordi hendelser i Windows Forms behandles sekvensielt utenfor bruker brukergrensesnittet (UI) trådens meldingskøen.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Launches the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application, if and only if it is a Windows Presentation Foundation-based application running in a Web browser.
trans-unit.target: Starter den [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmet hvis og bare hvis det er et Windows presentasjon Foundation-basert program som kjører i en webleser.

trans-unit.source: This method is valid only for Windows Presentation Foundation-based applications that can be hosted in a Web browser (that is, their deployment manifests define the `hostInBrowser` XML element).
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er bare gyldig for Windows presentasjon Foundation-baserte programmer som kan ligge i en webleser (det vil si deres distribusjon programmanifest definerer den `hostInBrowser` XML-elementet).

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.ObjectHandle"></xref> corresponding to the launched application.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.ObjectHandle"> </xref> tilsvarer startes programmet.

trans-unit.source: Downloads the deployment manifest of the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] application in the background, and raises an event when the operation has either completed or encountered an error.
trans-unit.target: Nedlastinger manifestet distribusjon av [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] programmet i bakgrunnen, og oppretter en hendelse når operasjonen er fullført eller det oppstod en feil.

trans-unit.source: To receive notification of when this event completes, create an event handler for the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en hendelsesbehandling for å bli varslet om når denne hendelsen er fullført, den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestCompleted>hendelsen.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestCompleted>

trans-unit.source: If this event is called, and no error is indicated by <xref:System.Deployment.Application.GetManifestCompletedEventArgs>, you should next call <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A> to verify that the application will have permission to run on the local computer.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne hendelsen kalles, og ingen feil angis av <xref:System.Deployment.Application.GetManifestCompletedEventArgs>, bør du neste kalle <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>å bekrefte at programmet har tillatelse til å kjøre på den lokale datamaskinen.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.GetManifestCompletedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the deployment manifest has been downloaded to the local computer.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når distribusjon manifestfilen er lastet ned til den lokale datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property of <xref:System.Deployment.Application.GetManifestCompletedEventArgs> to check whether <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A> completed successfully or returned an error.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>for <xref:System.Deployment.Application.GetManifestCompletedEventArgs>å se om <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>fullført eller returnerte en feil.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.GetManifestCompletedEventArgs> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> is null, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A> completed successfully, and you can call <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>er null, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A>ble fullført, og du kan ringe <xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A>.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.AssertApplicationRequirements%2A> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.InPlaceHostingManager.GetManifestAsync%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>
